199
00:10:19,866 --> 00:10:21,833
SORRY, DR. TOKIOKA.

200
00:10:21,900 --> 00:10:23,300
- CALL ME "T."

201
00:10:23,366 --> 00:10:25,233
MEN LIKE ME,
ARROGANT ENOUGH

202
00:10:25,300 --> 00:10:27,166
